<h1>Body Mass Index</h1>
<p>You're beautiful just the way you are.  But still, it is supposedly good to have all of the "<a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=106268439" target="_blank">facts</a>".</p>
<form action='/bmi' method='get'>
  <h2>Imperial</h2>
  Mass (lbs): <input type="number" step="any" name="imperial_mass">
  Height (in): <input type="number" step="any" name="imperial_height">
  <button>Calculate!</button>
  <h2>Metric</h2>
  Mass (kg): <input type="number" step="any" name="metric_mass">
  Height (m): <input type="number" step="any" name="metric_height">
  <button>Calculate!</button>
</form>

<% if @metric_result || @imperial_result%>
  <br>
    <% if @metric_result %>
      <p>Your BMI is <%= @metric_result.round(2) %>.
    <% elsif @imperial_result %>
      <p> Your BMI is <%= @imperial_result.round(2) %>.
    <% end %>
    Cheers to your continuing and/or improving good health!</p>
  <% else %>
<% end %>

  